but it's the same thing.

00:47:00.809 --> 00:47:03.539
You borrow money and the guy
promises you can confiscate

00:47:03.539 --> 00:47:05.030
something if he doesn't pay.
 

00:47:05.030 --> 00:47:07.949
Four thousand years and we
screwed it up.

00:47:07.949 --> 00:47:10.159
